    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a standard of excellence rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. We invite the most discerning buyers to experience this impeccable example of engineering and luxury.",
